  "remarks": "Sergey Gavrilchuk is Head of the Yunarmiya Regional Headquarters of the “Republic of Crimea” and a member of the United Russia Party. The All-Russia “Young Army” Military Patriotic Social Movement (Yunarmiya) is a Russian paramilitary organisation. In his capacity as the regional Head of Yunarmiya, he organises activities that promote military training and preparation of youth for military service in the Russian Army.",
